teachers who excelled in ethics education were honored in the
Great Hall of the People today.
</P>
<P>
Lei Jieqiong, vice-chairman of the Standing Committee of the
National People's Congress, Vice-Minister of the State Education
Commission Zhang Tianbao and Li Wenhai, president of the People's
University of China, presented cups as prizes and honorary
