remained unchanged at 816 cents and 352 cents respectively. The
gainers included Fletcher Energy, rising 6c to 686c, Lion Nathan
picking up 6c to 381c, and Air New Zealand gaining 1c to 281c.
</P>
<P>
But Brierley Investment lost 1c to 137c.
</P>
<P>
There were equal 44 rises and 44 falls.  
</P>
